  abstract  = "OBJECTIVE: Our purpose was to identify the impact of the
               physical status of the American Society of Anesthesiologists
               (ASA) on the 30-day readmission of patients receiving operative
               management of orthopaedic fractures using the National Surgical
               Quality Improvement Program (NSQIP) database. METHODS: We
