               readmissions in the combined population (odds ratio = 1.45, 95\%
               confidence interval = 1.13-1.88, P = 0.001). For the combined
               analysis, compared with patients with an ASA score of 1,
               patients with an ASA score of 2 were 1.04 times as likely to
